    <abstract>
      <p>MetalDetector identifies CYS and HIS involved in transition metal protein binding sites, starting from sequence alone. A major new feature of release 2.0 is the ability to predict which residues are jointly involved in the coordination of the same metal ion. The server is available at <ext-link ext-link-type="uri" xlink:href="http://metaldetector.dsi.unifi.it/v2.0/">http://metaldetector.dsi.unifi.it/v2.0/</ext-link>.</p>
